And there we go! This article aimed to provide a general overview of the basic syntax and structure of JavaScript. Weâ€™ve looked at many of the common conventions, however, remember you can be somewhat flexibleâ€Šâ€”â€Šespecially when working in collaborative environments with their own particular standards.

Syntax and structuring both have an important role the play for both the functionality of our programs as well as for code readability and maintainability.


